text:
Found this halal spot while waiting for bike repairs. Tried Burmese food for the first time and it was so good!
The burmese laksa is soo creamy (not spicy by default), but the chili fish floss gave it a little more kick.
Many dishes for you to choose from too. Wife had chicken with butter rice.

Nice staff and chill location
Had the Burmese laksa! It’s tastes so gentle and warming! 5 stars! ⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️ Definitely should try as there are not much halal Burmese food options, would come back! :D
Trying Burmese food? Here they are “Shiok Halal Cuisines” newly opened… find the fantastic taste…
Superb the best prata I have tasted. The briyani as well. Cheap and good!
Good place. Good food. The owner uncle is very polite.
